OL,3,CSir Kenny Dalglish fined for speeding
OL,4,Cin 20mph zone
OL,6,FLiverpool FC legend Sir Kenny Dalglish
OL,7,Fhas been fined #1,000 after he was
OL,8,Fcaught breaking a 20mph speed limit.
OL,10,FThe 74-year-old was prosecuted by
OL,11,FMerseyside Police after he was caught
OL,12,Fon a speed camera in the town of
OL,13,FCrosby last September.
OL,15,FSir Kenny, one of Liverpool's all-time
OL,16,Fgreats who won six league titles and
OL,17,Fthree European Cups during his playing
OL,18,Fdays, pleaded guilty to speeding and
OL,19,Fwas sentenced.
