OL,3,CSir Kenny Dalglish fined for speeding
OL,4,Cin 20mph zone
OL,6,FMagistrate Sylvia Yang gave him three
OL,7,Fpenalty points on his licence and
OL,8,Fordered that he pay a #1,000 fine,
OL,9,F#120 in costs, and a #400 victim
OL,10,Fsurcharge.
OL,12,FCourt papers show Sir Kenny was also
OL,13,Fcharged by the police with failing to
OL,14,Fidentity himself as the driver of the
OL,15,Fvehicle in the aftermath of the
OL,16,Fspeeding offence.
OL,18,FMerseyside Magistrates' Court was told
OL,19,FSir Kenny had not replied when first
OL,20,Fwritten to about the incident.
