OL,3,CSir Kenny Dalglish fined for speeding
OL,4,Cin 20mph zone
OL,6,FHowever, the former Scotland
OL,7,Finternational pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fthat offence, and wrote in a note to
OL,9,Fthe court: "I do not remember
OL,10,Freceiving the letter asking for the
OL,11,Finformation of the driver/rider of a
OL,12,Fvehicle."
OL,14,FThe police force then agreed to drop
OL,15,Fthe charge.
OL,17,FThe court was told Sir Kenny's
OL,18,Fspeeding offence happened at 2.09pm on
OL,19,FSeptember 21, 2025, as he drove his
OL,20,Fsilver Mercedes on Little Crosby Road
OL,21,Fat 30mph.
