OL,3,CSir Kenny Dalglish fined for speeding
OL,4,Cin 20mph zone
OL,6,FThe road has a 20mph limit as it
OL,7,Fpasses through the village area of
OL,8,FLittle Crosby.
OL,10,FKevin Scott, the safer roads manager
OL,11,Ffor Merseyside Police, told the court
OL,12,Fin a statement: "On September 24,
OL,13,F2025, a Notice of Intended Prosecution
OL,14,Fand a requirement to provide driver
OL,15,Fdetails under Section 172 of the Road
OL,16,FTraffic Act 1988 was sent by first
OL,17,Fclass pre-paid post to the registered
OL,18,Fkeeper, Kenneth Dalglish... who failed
OL,19,Fto comply with the Section 172
OL,20,Frequest."
