OL,6,FSir Kenny, who managed Liverpool to
OL,7,Fthree league titles and two FA Cup
OL,8,Ftriumphs ` and was knighted in 2018,
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to the speeding offence
OL,10,Fin writing, without needing to appear
OL,11,Fin court.
OL,13,FHe was prosecuted and sentenced in the
OL,14,FSingle Justice Procedure, a fast-track
OL,15,Fcourt process which enables
OL,16,Fmagistrates to deal with cases based
OL,17,Fon written evidence and behind closed
OL,18,Fdoors.
